  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user I want any gesture based interactions on mobile to be easily discoverable and provide me with feedback to know if my action is succesful.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\nIt ocasionally takes people multiple attempts to open the profile of someone in a public chat to invite them to a 1:1 chat. The tap area seems smaller than it needs to be and gives no feedback on tap. This issue is intended to review the design specification and implementation.\r\n\r\n*Type*: Usability issue\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nFor elements that are tappable to have a sufficiently large tap surface (44x44) and indicate whether they are selected.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nTap surface too small and not responsive\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\nUnclear if this issue is caused by design specs / implementation or both.\r\nIssue came up in UX testing RRR820180906T3I3.1\r\nhttps://docs.google.com/presentation/d/10qb5jRXwRT9lYkxrn8Ui5Bov_JRuf1WBaPqSXd0ZAtY/edit#slide=id.g41d28d5cd7_19_37\r\n\r\n\n\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/_vO60E7Z21r_Wt8D2EvcpUodrA1wl1klLexYshNEYeZK_zD30zGKxUXmt4JEUnlGwjOVjw=w1200-h630-p\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div>Google Docs</div><div><strong><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/10qb5jRXwRT9lYkxrn8Ui5Bov_JRuf1WBaPqSXd0ZAtY/edit?usp=embed_facebook\">Report RRR8 Chat & Command</a></strong></div><div>Hester Status 17 / 09 / 2018 UXR findings Chat & Command RRR8 Sept 6th 2018</div></blockquote>",
